Itomic Hosting Functions module for Drupal
------------------------------------------

Provides the following functionality:
  - Various helper functions for development and staging environments
  - Country array function
  - Debugging functions
  - Ability to force HTTPS for authenticated sessions and the login page
  - Reusable panels functionality

CHANGELOG:
  - Originally created sometime in 2010 (Alex)
  - Added to Git on 24/05/2011 (Alex)
  - HTTPS redirection added on 16/8/2011 (Nick)
  - Drupal 7 port on 11/9/2011 (Nick)
  - Split out functionality to submodules 11/10/2011 (Nick)

